{"tid":1483480,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"央視：止暴制亂的主流民意不可違","createTime":"2019-08-18T12:03:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T12:08:15.000Z","uid":53003,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"59a79ebb28a0951825ddc25619b55e8d2d66e954","tid":1483480,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T12:03:15.000Z","msg":"北京中央電視台在《新聞聯播》播放央視快評，強調止暴制亂的主流民意不可違。<br />\n<br />\n社評說，過去兩個多月以來，少數極端暴力分子肆意衝擊香港社會秩序，挑動對立、公然打砸燒，今天的東方明珠已是傷痕累累，滿目瘡痍。連日來，香港社會的善良和理智已經喚醒，越來越多人堅決向暴力說不，「沉默的大多數」不再沉默。<br />\n<br />\n社評又說，止暴制亂不僅是廣大香港同胞的共同心聲，也是14億中國人的一致心願。亂港暴力分子再怎麼鼓噪，也不過是迴光返照。亂港活動已經進入窮途末路，等待的是法律和正義的審判。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1475376-20190818.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1475376-20190818.htm&d=xzf4O3tGv54ZmzQe4QccrFcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=30392c48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1475376-20190818.htm&h=5beeb6ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1475376-20190818.htm</a>"},{"pid":"02d62795b2ed961e43de9cfbd9a19c2356e5214b","tid":1483480,"uid":122001,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T12:04:15.000Z","msg":"四十幾慢人民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44854b465a8ff93410ad318e328a0d3988637bfb","tid":1483480,"uid":165891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T12:08:15.000Z","msg":"拒對每個城市都可以話另外果幾十億唔支持你支持我.<br />\n代表人民群眾特技max"}]}